Jackyl is an American hard rock band formed in 1991. Their sound has been described as hard rock, heavy metal and Southern metal. Their eponymous album has sold more than a million copies in the United States.

Rowyco is the eighth studio album by American southern rock band Jackyl. Released on 5 August 2016, the album was published via Mighty Loud Records.
